<view class="page-shell login-page">
  <view class="page-orb page-orb-a"></view>
  <view class="page-orb page-orb-b"></view>

  <view class="login-hero">
    <text class="eyebrow">InkPi Cloud</text>
    <text class="hero-brand">云端记录</text>
    <text class="hero-copy">
      树莓派端完成评测后，结果会自动同步到这里。登录后即可查看每次得分、识别字和评价建议。
    </text>

    <view class="hero-points">
      <view class="hero-point">
        <text class="hero-point-title">实时同步</text>
        <text class="hero-point-text">无需手动导图，历史记录会自动刷新。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="hero-point">
        <text class="hero-point-title">移动查看</text>
        <text class="hero-point-text">在手机上快速回看评测结果，适合课堂与展示场景。</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="paper-panel login-panel">
    <view class="panel-head">
      <text class="panel-title">登录查看评测记录</text>
      <text class="panel-subtitle">演示账号已经预填，也可以点击下方按钮一键填入。</text>
    </view>

    <view class="demo-strip">
      <view class="demo-meta">
        <text class="demo-label">演示账号</text>
        <text class="demo-value">demo / demo123456</text>
      </view>
      <button class="ghost-btn demo-btn" bindtap="fillDemo">填入账号</button>
    </view>

    <view class="form-group">
      <text class="field-label">账号</text>
      <input
        class="field-input"
        placeholder="请输入账号"
        value="{{username}}"
        data-field="username"
        bindinput="onInput"
      />
    </view>

    <view class="form-group">
      <text class="field-label">密码</text>
      <input
        class="field-input"
        password
        placeholder="请输入密码"
        value="{{password}}"
        data-field="password"
        bindinput="onInput"
      />
    </view>

    <text wx:if="{{error}}" class="login-error">{{error}}</text>

    <button class="primary-btn login-btn" loading="{{loading}}" bindtap="onLogin">
      进入云端记录
    </button>
  </view>
</view>
